translations: adj.无证人签署的；未注意到的，未察觉到的

phrs.translation: 无证人签署的, 未注意到的
翻译, 无见证人签名的法律文件
目击与非目击认证测试

sentences.sentence: Your life will not go unwitnessed because I will be your witness.
sentences.translation: 你的生命不会不被见证，因为我将见证。

sentences.sentence: This unwitnessed signature was declined by the court as an evidence.
sentences.translation: 法庭拒绝拿这个无人证明的签名作为证据。

sentences.sentence: Vector acoustic field is a very important part of sound wave, but the vector information of acoustic wave has been unwitnessed for a long time.
sentences.translation: 矢量声场时声波场的重要组成部分，但在相当长的一段时间内没有受到重视，声波的矢量信息却被忽略了。
